description: The investment seeks to track the price and yield performance, before fees and expenses, of the Bloomberg Barclays Global Aggregate Enhanced Yield Index (USD Hedged). Normally, at least 80% of the fund's total assets (exclusive of collateral held from securities lending) will be invested in component securities of the index and investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the economic characteristics of such component securities. The index is designed to broadly capture the global investment grade, fixed income securities market. The fund is non-diversified.
name: WisdomTree Yield Enhanced Global Aggregate Bond Fund
